{
  "stem": "21731.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then there were three sisters, much older, they were Lady Caroline, and Lady Ann, and Lady something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For me that was all Chinese.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I couldn't understand all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When visitors came, they brought portions of tea with them, because tea was rationed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Grenfell had more tea than they have in China.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was quite-- they were very good to me, the Grenfells, very good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They loved both boys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They wanted them to eat at their table, which I never allowed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When they came-- Yan left, stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had a flat in the basement, two rooms and a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And naturally, enough food for Yan, also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He went-- George was already accepted at Bartholomew, but he had to wait a year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because there was no place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the best one, and a Pole, there be accepted was the best you can-- everybody who knows George now, knows, oh, you're a Bart's man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Yan was studying still at college, but was accepted then, at the Imperial College.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Engineering, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] aeronautical.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyway, I stayed with the Grenfells for a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were always very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to the Waldegrave Estate for summer, because the Waldegraves went for the summer to Scotland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed there with only the two of them, the old-- well, Colonel, and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Grenfell, and my little dog- I had a dog with me-- and a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Grenfell thought I may be very lonely there, so bring a friend with you, Eva.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was my stay with the Grenfells.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then they-- they let their flat in Pond Street, or Cadogan Place, to diplomats, and went to Betteshanger, which is in-- near Deal.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
